The,New,Zealand,Transport,Agency,s,InfoConnect,is,a,web,service,that,connects,developers,with,NZ,traffic,monitoring,systems,through,a,series,of,APIs,The,Christchurch,Traffic,API,is,accessible,via,both,SOAP,and,REST,protocols,and,exposes,two,sets,of,traffic,data,for,the,Christchurch,area,Road,works,Roadwork,locations,on,the,Christchurch,Roading,Network,including,duration,and,impact,details,Planned,public,events,Events,within,Christchurch,that,have,an,associated,temporary,traffic,management,plan,including,duration,and,impact,details